                              "id": "ebp4y",
                              "name": "aiP1",
                              "fill": "$foreground",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "好，用大白话解释这两个概念。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.7,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "wCzvD",
                              "name": "aiP2",
                              "fill": "$foreground",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "第一个问题：优先级怎么排\n\n\"优先级\"就是\"什么事情应该先做\"的意思。\n\n比如老板发的邮件催你今天下班前回复，那这封邮件优先级就最高。而一封通知下周团建的邮件，优先级就低一些。我会按紧急程度和重要性帮你排好。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.7,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "raV3n",
                              "name": "aiP3",
                              "fill": "$foreground",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "第二个问题：包含哪些渠道\n\n你目前连接了邮箱、企业微信和钉钉三个渠道。我会把这三个地方的未读消息和待办事项全部汇总到一起，同时也会把已读但未处理的邮件单独列出来，避免遗漏。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.7,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "29AGI",
                              "name": "aiP4",
                              "fill": "$foreground",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "问题出在哪里呢？出在优先级判断上。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.7,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "gxdzj",
                              "name": "aiP5",
                              "fill": "$foreground",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "假设你今天有20封未读邮件、5条钉钉待办、3个文档需要审批。如果不排序，你可能先处理了一封无关紧要的通知邮件，而忽略了老板要求今天必须回复的紧急合同审批。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.7,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "3wDc0",
                              "name": "aiP6",
                              "fill": "$foreground",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "这就是核心价值：帮你从海量信息中，快速找到最该先处理的事情，避免重要事项被淹没。",
                              "lineHeight": 1.7,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "600"
                            },
